  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nWhile solving #15018 on [this PR](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15110), @pavloburykh helped reporting the following problem:\r\n\r\nWhite screen appears for moment during redirection from Intro screen to I'm new to Status screen (IOS only)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nNot to show a white screen while navigating\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nWhite screen appears for moment during redirection from Intro screen to I'm new to Status screen (IOS only)\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Monosnap 2023-03-13 13-41-23\" width=\"364\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/224693275-66219999-bf64-4c70-9ab9-75a4504f756d.png\">\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/224693336-b9160323-9d8e-4a01-ae27-d84af1b69170.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\nSteps:\r\n\r\n  1. Install app\r\n  2. Open Intro screen\r\n  3. Tap Sign in/I'm new to Status button\r\n  4. Pay attention if white screen appears for moment during animation between screens\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Operating System: Reproducing on iPhone X, IOS 14.1\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
